MIRAMAR, Fla., May 26, 2011 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Spirit Airlines, Inc. (Nasdaq:SAVE) announced today that it has priced its initial public offering of 15,600,000 shares of common stock at a public offering price of $12.00 per share. Certain selling stockholders have granted the underwriters a 30-day option to purchase up to an additional 2,340,000 s...

